  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Purchase Notice</h2>This is a horror game with no saved single player experience. You will walk through a terrifying abandoned hospital from a first person perspective, exploring its past and why you appeared in this abandoned hospital.<br>There are not many scary points in the game settings, so you can consider it as a walking simulator for an abandoned hospital.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >story</h2>After waking up, you were locked in the basement of a eerie abandoned hospital. You need to find a way to leave the hospital and understand why you appeared in the hospital.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909560/extras/93c0be08d67f5ca3969ec25331bc694d.avif?t=1712820102\" width=620 height=374 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Time</h2>1 Hour to 1.5 Hours<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Decrypt</h2>The game decryption content is very simple. Follow the prompts to find the corresponding door key in order to get closer to the truth",
